          <comment xml:lang="en">Price calculated based on direct measure in 2022 of the consumption of the University of Barcelona plant and on costs of the inputs. Price shall be reconsidered depending on application, e.g. different region, full scale application, etc.
The price was converted to EUR based on the annual exchange rates published by the European Central Bank (https://sdw.ecb.europa.eu/quickview.do?SERIES_KEY=120.EXR.A.USD.EUR.SP00.A, last accessed on 2022-02-15) and adjusted for inflation relative to 2005 using the producer price index (PPI) of the euro area, published by eurostat (https://appsso.eurostat.ec.europa.eu/nui/show.do?dataset=sts_inpp_a&amp;lang=en, last accessed on 2022-05-04).</comment>
